pyramid Recruiting a Pirate Crew

inverted

Dockside Rabble blue
  Every drifter and deckhand who hears
  the call in the tavern.

Signed Articles cyan
  Those who make their mark on the
  ship's charter.

Proven in a Fight green
  Hands who held their post through
  the first broadside.

Trusted Mates orange
  The seasoned few fit to lead a
  boarding party.
